In ListView::doLayout size was wrong at the moment of layout changing. I caused wrong item position and wrong shift in jumpToItem.

Possible fix:
Was:

```
void ListView::doLayout()
{
...
    _innerContainer->forceDoLayout();
    updateInnerContainerSize();
    _innerContainerDoLayoutDirty = false;
}
```

Must be:

```
void ListView::doLayout()
{
...
    updateInnerContainerSize();
    _innerContainer->forceDoLayout();
    _innerContainerDoLayoutDirty = false;
}
```

Because simulator is base on libluacocos2d and libjscocos2d, so we combine them in one PR. 

There hasn't any functional modify in this PR, all changes in this PR is make libluacocos2d, libjscocos2d and libsimulator can be compiled as dynamic library and export functions needed by cocos studio. We have add function export declare to related function and modify some function implement method in simulator. In previous version, some function implement in simulator project, but call in libsimulator project, this cause libsimulator can not compiled as a dynamic library.

@ricardoquesada @dualface @minggo @pandamicro Please review this PR.
@linshun Does there still has somebody can help review simulator related modifies? Please help to assign them, Thanks.

ccs.load = function(file, path){
    var object = {
        node: null,
        action: null
    };
    object.node = ccs._load(file, null, path);    //load and prase once.
    object.action = ccs._load(file, "action", path);    //load and prase twice.
    if(object.action && object.action.tag === -1 && object.node)
        object.action.tag = object.node.tag;
    return object;
};
